theme_override_font_sizes/font_size = 13
text = "Helix Solutions was founded in 2014 by Richard Holt and James Kane with a single mission: to make financial compliance simpler, smarter, and more transparent.

What began as a two-person consultancy has grown into a team of over 140 professionals serving clients across the UK financial sector. We combine regulatory expertise with proprietary data tools to help our clients stay ahead of an increasingly complex compliance landscape.

We believe good governance isn't just a legal obligation — it's a competitive advantage."
